---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';

const heroStats = [
  { label: 'Cloud Cases', value: '50+', subtext: 'shipped to production' },
  { label: 'Deploy Speed', value: '≈79% faster', subtext: 'deployment turnaround' },
  { label: 'Mentored Teams', value: '15', subtext: 'engineer squads coached' },
  { label: 'Content', value: 'Debug Life', subtext: 'platform & community', href: 'https://www.youtube.com/@debuglife.indonesia' },
];

const playbook = [
  'Architect resilient AWS baselines',
  'Automate delivery with IaC & CI/CD',
  'Translate ops lessons into narratives'
];
---

<Layout title="Ian Yulianto - DevOps Engineer & AWS Cloud Specialist">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 animate-fade-in-up relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(255,255,255,1),rgba(245,245,245,0.4))]"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-10 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black/5 to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-10 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black/5 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 border border-black/5 bg-white/98 px-6 md:px-10 py-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch gap-12 shadow-[6px_6px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-8">
        <p class="accent-chip">Automation / Reliability / Storytelling</p>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1.05] text-black">
            DevOps Engineer &
            <span class="block italic text-black">AWS Cloud Specialist</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-black/70 mt-6 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            I turn brittle infrastructure into reliable systems, automate delivery, and document the lessons so teams can scale their impact.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <Button href="./projects/">See My Work</Button>
        <Button href="./contact/">Contact Me</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-4">
          {heroStats.map((stat) => (
            stat.href ? (
              <a
                href={stat.href}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="border border-black/10 bg-white/90 px-5 py-5 shadow-[8px_8px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer"
              >
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-black/50 flex items-center gap-2">
                  {stat.label}
                  {stat.label === 'Content' ? (
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-4 h-4">
                      <path fill="#FF0000" d="M21.8 8.001a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-1.758-1.77C18.25 6 12 6 12 6s-6.25 0-8.042.231A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.2 8.001 26.9 26.9 0 0 0 2 12a26.9 26.9 0 0 0 .2 3.999 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1.758 1.77C5.75 18 12 18 12 18s6.25 0 8.042-.231a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1.758-1.77A26.9 26.9 0 0 0 22 12a26.9 26.9 0 0 0-.2-3.999Z" />
                      <path fill="#ffffff" d="M10 15.2V8.8L15.5 12z" />
                    </svg>
                  ) : null}
                  <span class="text-[0.6rem]">↗</span>
                </p>
                <p class="text-3xl font-black mt-2 text-black">{stat.value}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-black/60">{stat.subtext}</p>
              </a>
            ) : (
              <div class="border border-black/10 bg-white/90 px-5 py-5 shadow-[8px_8px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-black/50">{stat.label}</p>
                <p class="text-3xl font-black mt-2 text-black">{stat.value}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-black/60">{stat.subtext}</p>
              </div>
            )
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 relative flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-y-4 right-8 w-px bg-black/10"></div>
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm">
          <img 
            src="./ian-hero.png" 
            alt="Ian Yulianto DevOps & Cloud Specialist" 
            class="relative z-10 w-full"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-0 border border-black/15 bg-white px-6 py-4 shadow-[10px_10px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-black/50">Execution Playbook</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-black/80">
            {playbook.map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 border border-black"></span>
                <span>{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="my-20 h-px bg-black/10 relative">
    <span class="accent-chip absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-white px-4">Capabilities</span>
  </div>

  <!-- What I Do Section -->
  <section class="mb-20 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">What I Do</h2>
    <p class="text-black/60 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl">
      I merge principled AWS architecture with hands-on coaching so engineering teams can deploy faster without gambling on reliability.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <Card title="DevOps & Infrastructure">
        Automation, CI/CD, IaC, container orchestration.
      </Card>
      <Card title="AWS Cloud Architecture">
        ECS/Fargate, Lambda, RDS, S3, VPC.
      </Card>
      <Card title="Debug Life Indonesia">
        Content platform and community spotlighting real-world DevOps lessons, mentoring, and career narratives.
      </Card>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="my-20 h-px bg-black/10 relative">
    <span class="accent-chip absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-white px-4">Projects</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Featured Projects Section -->
  <section class="mb-20 animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Featured Projects</h2>
    <p class="text-black/70 text-lg mb-8 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
      Every engagement blends DevOps rigor with AWS-native patterns and storytelling through Debug Life Indonesia. Whether it’s migrating regulated workloads to ECS, orchestrating serverless data flows, or documenting these wins for the community, the work is anchored in the same playbook: automate with empathy, design for scale, and narrate the lessons so other builders can replicate the impact.
    </p>
    <div class="border border-black/10 bg-white px-8 py-6 shadow-[6px_6px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">DevOps + AWS + Debug Life</h3>
      <p class="text-black/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Recent projects include AWS replatforming for commerce systems, resilient CI/CD pipelines for content teams, and a public narrative layer via Debug Life Indonesia so lessons move beyond the terminal. Dive into the case studies to see how production outcomes translate directly into community knowledge.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
      <Button href="./projects/">View All Projects</Button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Debug Life YouTube CTA -->
  <section class="mb-20 animate-fade-in-up delay-300 border border-black/10 bg-white px-8 py-10 shadow-[6px_6px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8">
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
        <p class="text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-black/50">Debug Life Indonesia</p>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">Watch the real-world DevOps stories.</h3>
        <p class="text-black/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I document AWS migrations, automation tactics, and career lessons through video breakdowns so teams can learn directly from production wins and setbacks. Subscribe to follow along with the latest case studies and community conversations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <Button href="https://www.youtube.com/@debuglife.indonesia" class="px-10">
          YouTube Channel
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
